reviewText: Well I own some of the Latinas gone crazy dvds and this one was a recycled version of previous dvd releases from wayne enterprises. Some of the girls here are not all that hot, in fact some are very obese and really have no business flashing anykind of parts otherwise covered by clothing. Some girls are cute and flash for a tenth of a second, which forces you to pause the dvd to get a real good look at the girls. IN addition to this you have some annoying guy holding the camera asking the girls to give him permission to you their image on LATINAS gone crazy. SO pretty much every shot the guy repeats the words slowly and the stupid girls more often then not always get the words wrong. The dvd lasts about 60 minutes and i believe it was filmed in SOuth padre island and the Mcallen texas area so be warned you may see your girlfriend here if not maybe your sister !
